{
  "texts": [
    "Baxter et al. [97] developed an information embedding scheme to increase the achievable rate by combining subpulse selection and differential PM.",
    "In addition, Ma et al. [45] used both waveform and antenna selection to improve the achievable rate.",
    "For the carrier-agile phased array radar, a signaling strategy based on frequency and spatial IM was developed by Huang et al. [46].• Fast time modulation.",
    "The above two signaling strategies are inter-pulse modulation, and the low PRF becomes the bottleneck of achievable rate improvement [39].",
    "Fortunately, intra-pulse modulation is expected to overcome this challenge by modulating the intra-pulse waveform."
  ]
}